description:
&lt;p&gt;An opportunity exists to join our team of motivated and enthusiastic registered Pharmacy Technicians. You will work with the Pharmacy Team in Stores, Dispensary and also at Ward Level.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You must be registered with the GPhC, or be undertaking a qualification that will enable you to register with the GPhC within the next 9 months.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We are an organisation that encourages ambition, values and talent and appreciates people who can bring something special to our environment.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We run in-house training for all areas of our service and are keen to provide developmental opportunities for our Pharmacy Technicians, to enable them to realise their full potential.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;If you are keen to join our team and have the ability to work well under pressure whilst maintaining high levels of accuracy, we would love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name Janice Wright&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title Pharmacy Operational Manager&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address janice.wright9@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number 01536 492572&lt;/p&gt;
